<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 03:14:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国监管机构要求大型银行加大对万科的支持力度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-regulators-ask-large-banks-step-up-support-vanke-sources-say-2024-03-11/</link><description>两名消息人士称，中国监管机构最近会见金融机构，讨论国有房地产开发商万科的问题，要求大型银行加大融资支持力度，并要求私人债务持有人讨论延期问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 03:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-regulators-ask-large-banks-step-up-support-vanke-sources-say-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>台湾最高安全官员称，中国试图使台湾附近的军事演习“正常化”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-trying-normalise-military-drills-near-taiwan-islands-top-security-official-2024-03-11/</link><description>台湾最高安全官员周一向国会表示，中国平均每 7 至 10 天在台湾附近进行一次“联合战备巡逻”，称中国军队正试图使台湾附近的演习“正常化”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 02:48:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-trying-normalise-military-drills-near-taiwan-islands-top-security-official-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国大使称在中国被判处死刑的澳大利亚作家可能永远不会被执行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-writer-sentenced-death-china-may-never-be-executed-says-chinese-2024-03-11/</link><description>中国驻澳大利亚大使周一表示，如果这位前民主博主不再犯下任何罪行，上个月对被监禁的澳大利亚作家杨恒均判处的死刑缓期执行可能不会执行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 02:38:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-writer-sentenced-death-china-may-never-be-executed-says-chinese-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>油价因中国需求担忧而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-fall-china-demand-worries-2024-03-11/</link><description>由于对中国需求放缓的担忧，周一油价延续上周跌势，但围绕中东和俄罗斯的地缘政治风险挥之不去，限制了跌幅。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 01:56:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-fall-china-demand-worries-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>韩国监管机构发现中国股票衍生品销售存在不当行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-watchdog-finds-wrongdoings-sales-china-equity-derivatives-2024-03-11/</link><description>韩国金融市场监管机构周一表示，发现销售与香港股市指数挂钩的衍生品的金融公司存在不当行为。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 01:12:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-watchdog-finds-wrongdoings-sales-china-equity-derivatives-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国大使称澳大利亚葡萄酒关税审查已步入正轨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-ambassador-says-review-into-tariffs-australian-wine-progressing-well-2024-03-11/</link><description>中国大使肖千周一表示，中国对澳大利亚葡萄酒关税的审查进展顺利，但他没有证实澳大利亚政府声称争端将于本月得到解决。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 00:32:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-ambassador-says-review-into-tariffs-australian-wine-progressing-well-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>由于日本央行考虑实行正利率，亚洲股市下滑，日元坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-11/</link><description>亚洲股市周一大幅下挫，而在美国通胀数据可能加速或推迟全球降息之前，美元显得脆弱。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 00:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-11/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：中国的通胀、资本流动趋势正在逆转吗？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-10/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 22:43:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-10/</guid></item><item><title>上海振华否认对美国港口构成网络安全风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/shanghai-zhenhua-denies-posing-cybersecurity-risk-us-ports-2024-03-10/</link><description>在美国国会委员会质疑这家中国国有企业运往美国的起重机的工作后，上海振华重工 (ZPMC) 周日表示，其起重机不会构成网络安全威胁。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 10:15:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/shanghai-zhenhua-denies-posing-cybersecurity-risk-us-ports-2024-03-10/</guid></item><item><title>沙特阿美看到中国需求增长，寻求更多投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/aramco-chief-sees-healthy-chinese-demand-looking-more-investments-2024-03-10/</link><description>沙特阿美首席执行官阿明·纳赛尔周日表示，该石油巨头正在寻找在中国投资的更多机会，他表示中国的石油需求强劲且不断增长。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 09:10:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/aramco-chief-sees-healthy-chinese-demand-looking-more-investments-2024-03-10/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚贸易部长称中国葡萄酒和龙虾贸易壁垒取得良好进展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/good-progress-chinese-wine-lobster-trade-barriers-says-australia-trade-minister-2024-03-10/</link><description>澳大利亚贸易部长唐·法雷尔 (Don Farrell) 周日表示，中国将于 3 月底完成对澳大利亚葡萄酒长达数年的关税审查，并正在审查对龙虾进口的限制。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 00:19:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/good-progress-chinese-wine-lobster-trade-barriers-says-australia-trade-minister-2024-03-10/</guid></item><item><title>赣锋锂业表示，中国锂市场将长期呈上升趋势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-lithium-market-set-long-term-uptrend-says-ganfeng-lithium-2024-03-09/</link><description>中国主要电池金属供应商赣锋锂业董事长表示，电池金属价格稳定将有利于中国锂行业，电池金属价格将长期上涨。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 08:07:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-lithium-market-set-long-term-uptrend-says-ganfeng-lithium-2024-03-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国警告总体就业压力尚未缓解</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-overall-pressure-employment-yet-ease-2024-03-09/</link><description>人力资源部长周六表示，中国仍面临结构性就业问题，总体就业压力尚未缓解，经济放缓将为 2024 年大学毕业生数量再创新高做好准备。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 08:05:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-overall-pressure-employment-yet-ease-2024-03-09/</guid></item><item><title>彭博社称，美国考虑将长鑫存储列入黑名单，以遏制中国芯片的发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-mulls-blacklisting-cxmt-curb-chinas-chip-advance-bloomberg-news-says-2024-03-09/</link><description>彭博社周五称，美国正在考虑对包括芯片制造商长鑫存储技术在内的多家中国科技公司实施制裁，以进一步限制中国先进半导体的发展。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 02:55:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-mulls-blacklisting-cxmt-curb-chinas-chip-advance-bloomberg-news-says-2024-03-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国消费者价格因农历新年季节性上涨而波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-feb-consumer-prices-rise-07-year-earlier-2024-03-09/</link><description>由于与农历新年相关的支出，中国的消费者价格在六个月内首次上涨，为这个正在努力应对消费者信心疲弱的世界第二大经济体提供了一些喘息的机会，而出厂价格再次下跌。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 01:47:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-feb-consumer-prices-rise-07-year-earlier-2024-03-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>